436
00:28:33.497 --> 00:28:35.997
And one more thing... you don't
speak to anybody in here.

437
00:28:36.074 --> 00:28:36.998
You understand that?

438
00:28:54.351 --> 00:28:56.693
Lucy! Time to go home.

439
00:28:57.780 --> 00:28:59.321
Hurry up.

440
00:29:13.186 --> 00:29:15.504
