450
00:29:52.893 --> 00:29:53.708
So...

451
00:29:55.245 --> 00:29:57.153
Okay. okay.
let me get you some water.

452
00:29:57.172 --> 00:29:59.080
Oh. that's so sweet.
but I'm just gonna

453
