507
00:35:12.545 --> 00:35:14.061
None of it's gonna be
traced back to us.

508
00:35:14.214 --> 00:35:17.115
Nothing will because
I'm taking care of it now.

509
00:35:17.901 --> 00:35:19.200
Tarik.

510
00:35:22.238 --> 00:35:24.414
Hey. I-I still have
